                  </persName>
            . I am the wife of the last witness. He gave me the note the prisoner brought, I endorsed it (looks at one) this is it. I am sure the prisoner is the man. I heard him give the address.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t18210214-42-person560">
                  JOSEPH 
                  BALL
               <interp inst="t18210214-42-person560" type="surname" value="BALL"></interp>
