                     <interp inst="t18210214-42-person560" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            . I collect rent of 18 houses, from Nos. 1 to 18, Whitehead's-buildings; there are 21 houses there. I do not know the prisoner. I never knew him to live there. It is also called Exeter-buildings. I go there two or three times a week.</p>
