                     <interp inst="t18210214-42-person567" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            . The note is forged in every respect. It is signed C. Tabro, but it is not his writing; the other is also forged.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t18210214-42-person568">
                  CHARLES 
                  TABOR
               <interp inst="t18210214-42-person568" type="surname" value="TABOR"></interp>
