                     <interp inst="t18210214-42-person568" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            . I am a signing clerk. The note is not signed by me; there is no other of my name.</p>
               <p>(read)</p>
               <p>Prisoner's Defence. I am a poor unfortunate man, out of work. Leary, who has pleaded guilty, gave me the note to get some refreshment. I did not know it was forged.</p>
               <p>
                  <rs id="t18210214-42-verdict277" type="verdictDescription">
